a và Jack's. Anh ấy sớm bắt đầu một cuộc phiêu lưu với những người bảo vệ của nhà vua để giải cứu công chúa, chỉ để thấy rằng một vùng đất thần thoại chứa đầy những người khổng lồ thực sự tồn tại.</p>","tmdb_id":81005,"cast":["Rachel Griffiths","Yoson An","Mojean Aria","Ian Meadows","Rhys Muldoon","Anna Samson","Xana Tang","Matt Nable"],"director":["David Caesar"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"81005","season":null,"vote_average":5.868,"vote_count":5131},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Rachel Griffiths","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Rachel Griffiths","tmdb_id":3052,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n7rKwLjZmbkBKWBwhj9SYzsRaF6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3052"},{"name":"Yoson An","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yoson An","tmdb_id":1305610,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2hYX4VOpJEGzaOrS9xwe8qPkKJQ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1305610"},{"name":"Mojean Aria","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mojean Aria","tmdb_id":1375499,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v5W5lpuAWSDVMokU0RKGkHDT2rj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1375499"},{"name":"Ian Meadows","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ian Meadows","tmdb_id":1184955,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pHdYHx3nsGbUmjBbxHUbTTbktu0.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1184955"},{"name":"Rhys Muldoon","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Rhys Muldoon","tmdb_id":88360,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oL5trIFX2GUJMogha17KQNzUmQp.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/88360"},{"name":"Anna Samson","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Anna Samson","tmdb_id":1515827,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oBw3u0nYr0SCUe1CJTg3fYArlDP.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1515827"},{"name":"Xana Tang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xana Tang","tmdb_id":571567,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1z2Nn5KSAq82yfsd7IXYxBMI3T2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/571567"},{"name"